{"tid":1583670,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"*********************請善用不推文回覆*********************","createTime":"2019-09-20T17:09:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T17:24:50.000Z","uid":51411,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c8f0f43d250f89567468b4e1f0eac69c8f9015a3","tid":1583670,"uid":51411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T17:09:30.000Z","msg":"不善文回覆都出左一排<br />\n唔知做乜鳩一大部分人都係唔撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n逢親係<br />\n1. 未Fact check Post<br />\n或者 <br />\n2. 釣魚post，例如「xxxxx點駁好？」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iAoTxRL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiAoTxRL.png&h=3f1aa260&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咪撚覆</span></span><br />\n一係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不推文回覆</span></span><br />\n<br />\n另外幫手勸吓啲執迷不悟既手足，覆到手軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"546148402cc2a2b7fdffcc1fee532026b1b37d5f","tid":1583670,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T17:09:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"82921ecb34af6dd6de82b7aea68d0ca3fa0b9a1f","tid":1583670,"uid":248105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T17:10:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"faba2e66f5e9b7c3735b7b795e47811a6d376bac","tid":1583670,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T17:11:59.000Z","msg":"隨便攞去用：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">想回廢文嘅請用不推文回覆<br />\n膠都費事派請上一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /